    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a newsletter curator for {{ $json.user.username }}.\n\nTheir topics of interest: {{ $json.user.topics }}\n\nHere are all available articles:\n{{ $json.articles.map(a => a.title + ' - ' + a.link + '\\n' + (a.contentSnippet || '')).join('\\n\\n') }}\n\nSelect the 5 most relevant articles for this user based on their topics. Be sure that your 5 most relevant articles have something to do withtheir topics. If they're not keep going.\nWrite a clean HTML newsletter with a title, a short summary for each article, and a clickable link. If the user have horoscope things in his topics you can send him 10 articles tho, only the most relevants ones.\nKeep it engaging and personalized.\nReturn ONLY the HTML code, no markdown, no backticks, no explanation.",
